&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;GDS K S ‚Äî &lt;a href="https://github.com/thegdsks" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;@thegdsks&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Founder at &lt;a href="https://glincker.com" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;Glincker&lt;/a&gt; / &lt;a href="https://askverdict.ai" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;AskVerdict AI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

